    title: "What Is a Side Gable Barn? Uses, Sizes, and Buying Guide",
    metaTitle: "What Is a Side Gable Barn? Sizes, Uses, and Buying Guide",
    description: "Call us to get your free pricing guide for a side gable barn. Learn about sizes, uses, and buying tips from Legacy Structures in Hudson Falls, NY.",
    image: "/images/blog/what-is-a-side-gable-barn-uses-sizes-and-buying-guide-668930.webp",
